        "notes": "<p><strong>Combat Notes:</strong> The troll will attack the nearest creature and press the assault relentlessly. It uses Thick Hide as a reaction when struck, and leads every round with Crushing Slam. It will not flee.</p><p><strong>Regeneration:</strong> Remind players after the first round that wounds are closing — the clock is ticking. Without fire or acid damage, attrition heavily favors the troll.</p>",
